    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 52 },
      "id": 103,
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## GPU device counters (DCGM)\nL4 TDP = **72 W**, stock max proc clock = **2040 MHz**. Sustained power ≥ 65 W with proc clock ≤ 1500 MHz is the **power-capped** signature. See sie-perf-lab/docs/l4-cluster-perf-tuning.md §6.\n\n**MFU proxies** (below): `DCGM_FI_PROF_SM_ACTIVE` ≈ fraction of cycles an SM has ≥1 warp assigned (saturation). `DCGM_FI_PROF_PIPE_FP16_ACTIVE` + `PIPE_TENSOR_ACTIVE` = fraction of cycles the FP16/HMMA pipes are computing — our embedding model runs FP16 so `PIPE_FP16_ACTIVE` ≫ `PIPE_TENSOR_ACTIVE` is expected on varlen flash-attn."
      }
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 54 },
      "id": 30,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "mean"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.0.0",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "watt",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 55 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 68 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg(DCGM_FI_DEV_POWER_USAGE{namespace=\"$namespace\"}) by (pod)",
          "legendFormat": "{{pod}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "GPU power draw (72W TDP)"
    },
