    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 70 },
      "id": 34,
      "description": "DCGM_FI_PROF_SM_ACTIVE is the ratio of cycles at least one warp is resident on an SM — the right 'GPU saturated?' signal (DCGM_FI_DEV_GPU_UTIL above is the coarse nvidia-smi one). Sustained ≥0.9 with tensor/FP16 pipe ≥0.4 means the L4 is compute-bound on tensor ops.",
